headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week’s Car Meet Prize Ride: The Karin Sultan RS Classic
content: Join in the fun with your fellow speed freaks and LS Car Meet members by placing in the Top 5 of 12 Street Race Series over the course of the next seven days to earn the keys to this week’s Prize Ride: the Karin Sultan RS Classic, a sensible sedan that moonlights as a customizer’s pipe-dream.
